channel.title: First Guitar Model!
channel.description:
This is my first Guitar model. Its a Gibson EDS-1275.
Heres the first Render. [IMG]http://i393.photobucket.com/albums/pp11/leavenow1/Gibsondoubleneck.png[/img]
Second [IMG]http://i393.photobucket.com/albums/pp11/leavenow1/Gibsondoubleneck1.png[/img] And the framework. If anyone is wondering so far it has 3762 faces.
[IMG]http://i393.photobucket.com/albums/pp11/leavenow1/Framework.png[/img]
It is not finished but this is most of it. Some of it is 3D, the switches and the jack are not 3D. No strings, fret inlay's, screws, the clip for a strap, and tuning pegs yet, and the body has not been curved just made 3D.
Rate or hate.
